{"TopicId":193868,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to reset the scenarios","CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-14T15:06:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-14T15:06:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI play on the ps4\u00A0, and I went into the scenarios when I\u00A0first got the game and totally screwed them up. Does anyone know how to reset the scenarios so i can do them again?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-14T17:34:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, on PC there is a \u0022Restart\u0022 button in the lower left of the window where you can choose which scenario you want to play.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-26T20:29:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223785281\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193868\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589477697\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197939\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AHHans\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/14/2020 at 12:34 PM, AHHans said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, on PC there is a \u0022Restart\u0022 button in the lower left of the window where you can choose which scenario you want to play.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks...but I do play on console...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-27T00:46:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223791480\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193868\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221590524950\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203745\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lewie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Lewie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks...but I do play on console...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a button on the console that resets the scenarios. When you are just restarting a particular scenario, look really carefully at the very first screen after you select the scenario. It\u0027ll tell you exactly which button to push.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}